com.thinkaurelius.titan.util.stats

Class ObjectAccumulator<K>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thinkaurelius.titan.util.stats.ObjectAccumulator<K>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - 

    public class ObjectAccumulator<K>
extends Object
    This class counts arbitrary objects of type and tries to do so efficiently in time and space. The class offers methods to increase the count of an object by a specified amount or default 1, as well as retrieving the number of times and object has been counted.
    Author:
    Matthias Broecheler
